    "# RNX 0.6 — Integrating RNAPro (Pipeline) v0.6\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Dual-source TBM** — Bio affine-gap aligner over train/val + 8,600 PDB_RNA CIF chains.  \n",
    "   RNAPro-style consensus blend of top-3 templates for slot-0 prediction.\n",
    "2. **RNet2-augmented Protenix** — Exactly replicating the RNAPro Methods:  \n",
    "   - Load frozen RNet2 (48 layers, d=384 single, d=128 pair)  \n",
    "   - Run `get_embeddings()` → weighted-average all-layer single + pair reps  \n",
    "   - Inject into Protenix via learned sigmoid gating on single + pair streams  \n",
    "   - USE_RNA_MSA=true, CHUNK_OVERLAP=256\n",
    "3. **Physics post-processing** — 3 passes bond/avoidance correction on all predictions.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Hyperparameters (all evidence-based):** OVERLAP=256, PASSES=3, MIN_PCT_ID=40, TOP_N=50\n"
   ]
  },
